{"tid":1170773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=勇武！工作問題爭執　食肆員工遭同事爆樽扑傷頭","createTime":"2019-05-25T08:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T10:17:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62610887ab0eb4c1811ca33c974aee6cfe18d17d","tid":1170773,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:41:51.000Z","msg":"九龍城太子道西456號一食肆發生傷人案。昨日(24日)深夜11時許，一名43歲姓黃男職員在上址因工作問題，與44歲姓張男同事起爭執，期間，事主遭對方用玻璃樽襲擊。警方接報到場，將2人分開，黃男頭部受傷，清醒送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n警員經調查後，將涉嫌傷人的張男拘捕，案件交九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190525/bkn-20190525040216872-0525_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190525%2Fbkn-20190525040216872-0525_00822_001.html&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62MRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e3fcd05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190525/bkn-20190525040216872-0525_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c14cdd498840a01d41470aca46c2944a61dade41","tid":1170773,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"香港人只有返工最勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cba4fc1bae807f65494b17a77749221e0b7a2ba","tid":1170773,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c14cdd498840a01d41470aca46c2944a61dade41","tid":1170773,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"香港人只有返工最勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"db988b8014d9389111414a0dd51ded5e717ac397","tid":1170773,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"返工 = ?"}]}